OL,6,FYouTube is now the second most-watched
OL,7,Fmedia service in the UK behind the BBC
OL,8,Fand ahead of ITV, according to an
OL,9,Fannual Ofcom report.
OL,11,FOverall, people spent an average of
OL,12,Ffour hours and 30 minutes a day
OL,13,Fwatching TV and video content at home
OL,14,Fin 2024, with broadcast TV still
OL,15,Fmaking up 56% of in-home viewing, the
OL,16,Fregulator said.
