OL,3,CYouTube now the second most-watched
OL,4,Cmedia service in the UK ` Ofcom
OL,6,FHowever, YouTube is "leading the
OL,7,Fcharge" in the streaming takeover of
OL,8,FTV sets, with the service now the
OL,9,Ffirst place younger viewers go as soon
OL,10,Fas they switch on.
OL,12,FAt home, people spent 39 minutes a day
OL,13,Fon YouTube in 2024, with 16 minutes of
OL,14,Fthis on the household's TV set.
OL,16,FYounger adults aged 16 to 34 are
OL,17,Fdriving the trend, watching 18 minutes
OL,18,Fof YouTube a day on TV, while one in
OL,19,Ffive children aged four to 15 (20%)
OL,20,Fhead straight to the app as soon as
OL,21,Fthey turn the set on.
