OL,6,FEven those aged over 55 have almost
OL,7,Fdoubled the time they spend watching
OL,8,FYouTube on their TVs compared with the
OL,9,Fprevious year ` up from six minutes a
OL,10,Fday in January 2023 to 11 minutes in
OL,11,FDecember.
OL,13,FYouTube's soaring popularity comes as
OL,14,Fthe platform's content has evolved,
OL,15,Fwith half of its top-trending videos
OL,16,Fnow more closely resembling
OL,17,Ftraditional TV, including long-form
OL,18,Finterviews and game shows, Ofcom said.
