OL,6,FOn average, people spent 4% less time
OL,7,Fwatching broadcast TV on TV sets than
OL,8,Fin 2023, with their average viewing
OL,9,Fdropping to two hours and 24 minutes a
OL,10,Fday, according to the report.
OL,12,FJust as in 2023, a decline was seen
OL,13,Facross all age groups except adults
OL,14,Faged 75 and over.
OL,16,FEd Leighton, Ofcom's interim group
OL,17,Fdirector for strategy and research,
OL,18,Fsaid: "Scheduled TV is increasingly
OL,19,Falien to younger viewers, with YouTube
OL,20,Fthe first port of call for many when
OL,21,Fthey pick up the TV remote.
